 Park Project\",\"color\":\"\",\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/db.silkroad.news.cn\\/en\\/2016\\/0329\\/100648.shtml\",\"subtitle\":\"\",\"suburl\":\"\",\"thumb\":\"\",\"description\":\"I. Project Briefing:The project\\u2019s planned use of land is 506 mu with 340.791 mu has been settled, which is under preparation of public land leasing. The project size is 10 million sets of fastener, 100,000 sets of bridge bearing, 260,000 sets of GRP sleeper, 1.25 million sets of shock-absorbing shoe, and 1600 sets of high-speed rail turnout. The main construction includes R&D and office building, workshops and related production lines. II. Total Investment & Expected Foreign Capital:The estimated total investment of the project is over RMB 10 billion, occupying land of 2000 mu. The project is to be constructed in three stages. The first stage is the on-going Tieke Yichen high-speed train heavy-load parts project with planned investment of RMB 3 billion; The second stage is to build achievements transformation base by cooperation with the Railway Research Institute and Metals & Chemistry Research Institute of China Academy of Railway Science, with planned investment of RMB 5 billion, occupying land of 1000 mu; The third stage is settlement of following projects with planned investment of RMB 3 billion, occupying land of 500 mu. When the project is informal production, the estimated average output value will achieve over RMB 8 million\\/mu while tax RMB 400,000\\/mu.Proposed utilization of foreign capital is over RMB 7 billion and domestic capital RMB 3 billion. III. Opportunities & Favorable Conditions:To support the Tieke Yichen high-speed train heavy-load parts R&D base to get bigger and stronger, the Development Zone handles special cases with special methods by launching land purchase reserve mechanism and 500 mu land is reserved for related supporting industry. Currently, communication with the farmers whose land will be acquired is on-going. IV. Evaluation of Economic Benefit:When in production, the estimated annual sales income is RMB 4 billion and tax RMB 200 million. V. Introduction of the Chinese Partner:Hebei Yichen Industry Group Co., Ltd., located in Yichen Street of Gaocheng Economic Development Zone, was established in 1985, occupying land of 173,000 m2 with total construction area of 120,000 m2, registered capital of RMB 100.35 million and 2000 employees among which 293 are professionals. The five varieties of type I spring fastener (spring, gauge block, screw spike, nut and flat washer) gained the production permit issued by the Ministry of Railway in 2002, type III spring has passed the check by the Ministry of Railway, big adjustment gauge block is the first innovative product in China, especially the casting workshops all use electric furnace to achieve zero pollution discharge. Special passenger line product is selected as one of the six integrators by the Ministry of Railway. In September 2002, the Company passed testing capacity verification required by GB\\/T15481:2000 and ISO\\/ITC 17025 by China Quality Inspection Association and acquired Enterprise Quality Inspection Organization Certificate of Qualification. In March 2003, the Company passed ISO9001\\uff1a2000 and ISO9001:2000 quality management system certification. The products are sold nationwide and countries and regions including US, Australia, Canada, Mexico, New Zealand, Russia and Hong Kong. The Company\\u2019s good credibility is renowned at home and abroad, and has been awarded the honorable title of National integrity & Law-abiding Town Enterprise, Model Family of Employees by ACFTU, Consumers Trust Units in Hebei Province, Excellent Private Scientific Enterprise, Contract-abiding and Good Credibility Enterprise, Civilization Unit, Superior Credibility Unit in Shijiazhuang, Top 10 Private Enterprises, Top 20 Industrial Enterprises of Gaocheng City, Model Tax Payment Enterprise and Excellent Basic-level Party Organization. VI. Approaches of Cooperation: Cooperation Disclaimer: The project is for reference only, please check the authenticity, accuracy and feasibility of the project before investment.\",\"time\":1459232713},{\"contentid\":100633,\"icon\":\"blank\",\"iconsrc\":\"\",\"title\":\"Project of Annual Production of 1 Million Tons of Methanol to Olefins (MTO)\",\"color\":\"\",\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/db.silkroad.news.cn\\/en\\/2016\\/0328\\/100633.shtml\",\"subtitle\":\"\",\"suburl\":\"\",\"thumb\":\"\",\"description\":\"I. Project Briefing:MTO is an important part of coal-based energy & chemical engineering industry in China, and coal-based olefin has become the second source of olefin at present. Since characteristics of energy (rich in coal and poor in oil resources) in China have determined that it is necessary for sustainable development of national economy to rely on adjustment and optimization of energy structure to reduce dependency upon oil resources, energetically develop new and high-tech products of coal chemical industry, and substitute coal chemical industry for petrochemical industry, coal-based olefin will become future development tendency. MTO technology of methanol to ethylene and propylene and MTP technology of methanol to propylene are important chemical technologies. At present, relatively mature technologies developed and researched at home and abroad mainly include MTO technology jointly developed by UOP and StatoilHydro, DMTO technology developed independently by Dalian Physical & Chemical, MTP technology developed by LURGI, and FMTP technology developed independently by Tsinghua University. The technologies mainly involve methanol conversion unit and olefin recovery unit, byproduct butene and carbon-rich fuel gas. The project construction period is three years. II. Total Investment & Expected Foreign Capital:The total project investment is about USD 560 million, construction investment USD 460 million, and working fund USD 100 million. The source of fund is sole foreign investment or funds raised by enterprises personally. III. Market Analysis:Low carbon olefin including ethylene and propylene is important basic chemical material, with annual demand growth rate being about 5%. It is predicted that ethylene and propylene equivalent demand at home in 2015 will reach 38 million and 28 million tons respectively, but self-sufficiency rate at home is only 60% at present, so mass import is necessary. Construction of MTO project can greatly reduce demand for olefin at home, and reduce dependency upon foreign imports.Olefin is important upstream raw material of Cangzhou Port-neighboring Economic and Technological Development Zone, and of great significance for integration of upstream and downstream of the development zone. The 630,000 tons\\/year PVC project of Hebei Jinniu Chemical Industry within the Port-neighboring Development Zone demands 400,000 tons of ethylene, together with demand of downstream projects for ethylene including styrene and vinyl acetate within the zone, ethylene gap has exceeded 1 million tons\\/year; the acrylate project of Cangzhou Badefu Chemical Industry and Huyi Chemical Industry within the zone is 380,000 tons\\/year, total acrylic acid and ester of many acrylate enterprises under negotiation is about 1 million tons\\/year, and upstream propylene demand reaches 800,000 tons\\/year; the development zone currently proposes to introduce fund to ethylene oxide and epoxy propane project, so mass upstream raw material olefin is required. Therefore, investment in project of coal to olefin in the Port-neighboring Economic and Technological Development Zone has abroad market prospect. IV. Opportunities & Favorable Conditions:The proposed project site is in the east of Cangzhou Port-neighboring Development Zone to realize night-connection and one-leveling, i.e., connection to upstream, downstream, rainwater, steam, industrial gas, natural gas, power, road and communication, and land leveling. The transportation is convenient, Jinghu Expressway, Rongwu Expressway, Shihuang Expressway and Coastal Expressway circling around; Jinhu Railway and Huangwan Railway crossing the north and south; Shuohuang Railway and Canggang Railway passing through the east and west; National Road 307, National Road 205 and Haifang Road constituting land transportation network extending in all directions. Beijing-Shanghai High Speed Railway reduces the time travelling from Cangzhou to Beijing and to Shanghai to 51 minutes and 4 and a half hours respectively. The 2-hour economic circle based on the development zone includes Beijing, Tianjin, Hebei and Shandong International Airports.The main material methyl alcohol is in abundant supply, distance between the Port-neighboring Development Zone and methyl alcohol export places including Erdos and Yulin is 600km, the bus transport is convenient, and port advantages may be taken to import methyl alcohol from abroad. Therefore, there is abundant material of methyl alcohol to invest in the project of coal to olefin in the development zone. V. Evaluation of Economic Benefit:Annual realizable sales revenue is USD 1.34 billion, and total realizable taxes and profits are USD 270 million. The return on investment is 22.60%, internal rate of return 30.74%, and recovery period 7 years. VI. Approaches of Cooperation:\\u00a0Solely foreign-invested Disclaimer: The project is for reference only, please check the authenticity, accuracy and feasibility of the project before investment.\",\"time\":1459126878}]',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<div class=\"b-tit-box mar-t-10\">\n    <h3 class=\"b-h3 \"><a href=\"javascript:;\">Key Projects</a>\n    </h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"bd\">\n    <ul class=\"list-zd\">\n    {loop $data $r}\n        <li><h3><a href=\"{$r[\'url\']}\" target=\"_blank\">{$r[\'title\']}</a></h3>\n            <div class=\"price\"><em>{table(\'item\',$r[\'contentid\'],\'itemsum\')}</em><br>Investment Amount</div>\n            <a href=\"\" class=\"talk\" style=\"display:none;\"></a>\n            \n       